column20: Prominent throughout - went second after 3 out - not fluent 2 out - challenging approaching last - ridden to lead after last - went clear inside final 110yds(tchd 4/1)
Soon led - faced challenge approaching last - headed after last - kept on(op 10/1)
In touch with leaders - went third approaching last - kept on - no match for first two(op 9/1 tchd 7/1)
Towards rear - headway 4 out - went third after 2 out - no extra and lost third approaching last(op 12/1 tchd 16/1)
Towards rear - headway before 2 out - kept on run-in - never on terms(op 8/1 tchd 9/1)
Towards rear - not fluent 9th - kept on from last - never near to challenge(op 16/1)
Prominent - mistake 9th - awkward jump 2 out - weakened approaching last(op 13/2 tchd 15/2)
Towards rear - dropped to rear 7th - detached 4 out(op 8/1 tchd 11/1)
Never better than midfield - outpaced 2 out - pulled up approaching last(op 6/1 tchd 5/1)
Towards rear - midfield after 4th - brought down 3 out(op 11/1 tchd 10/1 and 14/1)
